##一、环境准备 
###1、节点部署
192.168.24.4 mesos-dn1
安装的服务 mesos-master，mesos-slave，marathon，zookeeper，docker
###2、设置名字
	hostnamectl set­hostname mesos-dn1
###3、vi /etc/hosts:
	192.168.24.4 mesos-node1 mesos-dn1
###4、免密钥:
	ssh­keygen ­t rsa ­P ''
	scp /root/.ssh/id_rsa.pub root@mesos-dn1:/root/.ssh/authorized_keys
	chmod 600 /root/.ssh/authorized_keys
###4.2 yum 原配置;
	yum -y install wget
####添加阿里云yum 
	wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo
####添加mesosphere源
	sudo rpm -Uvh http://repos.mesosphere.com/el/7/noarch/RPMS/mesosphere-el-repo-7-1.noarch.rpm
###5、临时关闭SELinux 
	setenforce 0
	getenforce
###5.2 永久修改selinux:
	/etc/selinux/config
	
将 SELINUX=enforcing 修改为 SELINUX=disabled 重启生效
###6、关闭防火墙
	systemctl stop firewalld
	systemctl disable firewalld
###7、安装java8
	yum -y install java-1.8.0-openjdk.x86_64
	
##二、安装docker 
###1、利用yum安装docker
	yum -y install docker
###2、修改仓库地址
	vim /etc/docker/daemon.json
	{
	  "registry-mirrors": ["https://registry.docker-cn.com"]
	}
	systemctl restart docker.service
	# 若仍不生效: shutdown -r now
###2、启动docker
	systemctl start docker.service
###3、加入开机自启动服务
	systemctl enable docker.service
##三、安装zookeeper;
###1、进入源码安装目录下载zookeeper稳定版3.4.9并安装
	cd /usr/local/src/
	wget https://archive.apache.org/dist/zookeeper/zookeeper-3.4.9/zookeeper-3.4.9.tar.gz
	tar zxvf zookeeper-3.4.9.tar.gz
	mv zookeeper-3.4.9 /usr/local/
###2、创建软连接，方便以后升级时用
	ln -s /usr/local/zookeeper-3.4.9/ /usr/local/zookeeper
###3、修改zookeeper配置文件
	cd /usr/local/zookeeper/conf
	mv zoo_sample.cfg zoo.cfg
	vim zoo.cfg;
		-
		tickTime=2000
		initLimit=10
		syncLimit=5
		dataDir=/usr/local/zookeeper/data
		dataLogDir=/usr/local/zookeeper/logs
		clientPort=2181
		server.1=mesos-dn1:2888:3888­
###4、创建dataDir和dataLogDir目录
	mkdir -p /usr/local/zookeeper/data /usr/local/zookeeper/logs
###5、创建myid文件:
	echo "1" > /usr/local/zookeeper/data/myid
###6、启动zookeeper
	cd /usr/local/zookeeper
	./bin/zkServer.sh start
###7、检查服务启动情况
	ss -ntpl | grep :2181
###8、尝试连接zookeeper 
	./bin/zkCli.sh
	
##四、安装mesos: 
###1、安装mesos和marathon
	sudo yum -y install mesos
	yum -y install marathon.x86_64
###2、增加zookeeper的配置:
	touch /etc/mesos/zk
	echo "zk://192.168.24.4:2181/mesos" > /etc/mesos/zk
###3、mesos-master:
	touch /etc/mesos-master/quorum
	echo 1 > /etc/mesos-master/quorum
	touch /etc/mesos-master/ip
	echo "192.168.24.4" > /etc/mesos-master/ip
	touch /etc/mesos-master/hostname
	echo "192.168.24.4" > /etc/mesos-master/hostname
###4、mesos-slave:
	touch /etc/mesos-slave/ip
	echo "192.168.24.4" > /etc/mesos-slave/ip
	touch /etc/mesos-slave/hostname
	echo "192.168.24.4" > /etc/mesos-slave/hostname
####配置docker启动
	echo 'docker,mesos' > /etc/mesos-slave/containerizers
	echo '5mins' > /etc/mesos-slave/executor_registration_timeout
###5、marathon:
	mkdir -p /etc/marathon/conf/ && touch hostname
	echo 192.168.24.4 | sudo tee /etc/marathon/conf/hostname
###6、配置开机自启动
	systemctl enable mesos-master mesos-slave marathon
	systemctl start mesos-master mesos-slave marathon
###7、检验有没有安装成功
	mesos: 192.168.24.4:5050
![Mesos界面][mesos]

	marathon: 192.168.24.4:8080
![Marathon界面][marathon]	
###8、运行一个mesos任务来测试
	MASTER=$(mesos-resolve `cat /etc/mesos/zk`)
	mesos-execute --master=$MASTER --name="cluster-test" --command="sleep 60"
####打开浏览器查看

##五、elastic-job-cloud: 运维平台安装:
###1、下载源代码
	https://gitee.com/elasticjob/elastic-job.git
###2、elastic-job-cloud-scheduler maven 打包，生成
	elastic-job-cloud-scheduler-2.1.5.tar.gz
###3、上传到linux中，解压;进入conf;配置文件:
	elastic-job-cloud-scheduler.properties
	hostname=192.168.24.4
	mesos_url=zk://192.168.24.4:2181/mesos
	zk_servers=192.168.24.4:2181
	zk_namespace=elastic-job-cloud 
	http_port=8898

##六。在elastic-job cloud上发布app和作业
###1、建立项目，仿照官方文档elastic-job-cloud-example. 
###2、引入依赖：
	<dependency>
		<groupId>com.dangdang</groupId>
		<artifactId>elastic-job-cloud-executor</artifactId>
		<version>2.1.5</version>
	</dependency>
###3、作业开发:
	public class MyElasticJob implements SimpleJob {
		public void execute(ShardingContext shardingContext) {
			System.out.println(new Date() + "job名称" + shardingContext.getJobName()
					+ “分片数量”+ shardingContext.getShardingTotalCount()
					+ “当前分区” + shardingContext.getShardingItem()
					+ “当前分区名称” + shardingContext.getShardingParameter()
					+ “当前自定义参数” + shardingContext.getJobParameter() + "=============start==============");
		}
	}
###4、Java启动方式
```java
public class JobDemo {
	public static void main(final String[] args) {
		JobBootstrap.execute();
	}
}
```
###5、打包生成tar.gz文件，上传到linux. 
####项目案例文件
TestJob3 
<a href="https://gitee.com/xugy/xugy-matrix/raw/master/docs/tar/TestJob3.tar.gz">点此下载</a>
###6、在linux上安装一个httpd,做成一个文件服务器，将testJob.tar.gz，确保能够通过访问到这个文件。
	yum -­y install httpd
	systemctl start httpd.service
	scp TestJob4.tar.gz root@192.168.24.4:/var/www/html/abc
###7、发布APP
	curl -l -H "Content-type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"appName":"foo_app","appURL":"http://192.168.24.4/abc/TestJob4.tar.gz","cpuCount":0.1,"memoryMB":64.0,"bootstrapScript":"bin/start.sh","appCacheEnable":true,"eventTraceSamplingCount":0}' http://192.168.24.4:8899/api/app
###8、发布作业:
	curl -l -H "Content-type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"jobName":"foo_job","appName":"foo_app","jobClass":"com.dangdang.MyElasticJob","jobType":"SIMPLE","jobExecutionType":"TRANSIENT","cron":"0/5 * * * * ?","shardingTotalCount":3,"cpuCount":0.05,"memoryMB":16.0}' http://192.168.24.4:8899/api/job/register
